value.title: Jill Biden says her doctorate is among her proudest achievements: 'I worked so hard for it'

value.title: Covid: US Vice-President Mike Pence to receive vaccine

value.title: Virginia gubernatorial candidate says ‘Trump should declare martial law’

value.title: Biden picks Deb Haaland for Interior, AOC praises the 'progressive' move

value.title: Biden appears in campaign ad for Georgia's Jon Ossoff and Raphael Warnock

value.title: What comes next for a Donald Trump impersonator? J-L Cauvin has thoughts

value.title: Exclusive: New agreement needed to revive Iran nuclear deal under Biden, IAEA chief says
value.excerpt: Reviving Iran's nuclear deal under U.S. President-elect Joe Biden would require striking a new agreement setting out how Iran's breaches should be reversed, U.N. atomic watchdog chief Rafael Grossi said.

value.title: Election 2020 Today: Pence to Georgia, Biden’s climate team

value.title: U.N. Security Council to talk Western Sahara after Trump policy switch
value.excerpt: The U.N. Security Council is planning to discuss Western Sahara on Monday, diplomats said, after U.S. President Donald Trump recognized Morocco's sovereignty over the disputed region in return for the kingdom normalizing ties with Israel.

value.title: United States hopes for trade deal with UK, Trump's trade chief says - BBC
